#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga "
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Vijjāsutta "
msgstr "18. Knowledge "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.430, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.18:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.18:1.2"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’. "

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, vijjā; "
msgstr "What is knowledge? "

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.18:1.5"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhe ñāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye ñāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe ñāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ—"
msgstr "“Knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, vijjā; "
msgstr "This is called knowledge. "

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotīti. "
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.18:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.18:2.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
